trans-unit.source: Implements <xref:System.IserviceProvider> and provides access to services offered by the editing context.
trans-unit.target: Implementerer <xref:System.IserviceProvider>og gir tilgang til tjenester som tilbys av redigering konteksten.</xref:System.IserviceProvider>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Services%2A> represent functionality that is either provided by the host for the designer to use or that is used by the designer to make functionality available to all designers within the editor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Services%2A>representere funksjonaliteten som tilbys av verten for utformeren for å bruke enten eller som brukes av utformeren til å gjøre funksjonaliteten tilgjengelig for alle utviklere i redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Services%2A>

trans-unit.source: It is obtained from the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext> by the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Services%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Det er hentet fra den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext>av den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Services%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext.Services%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.EditingContext>
